(44, 13, 24, 44, 1, 22, 22, NULL, 'Connection of John''s Baptism', 'Both passages emphasize the significance of the baptism of John as a foundational event in the ministry of Jesus. Acts 13:24 mentions John''s preaching of repentance, while Acts 1:22 references the necessity of this baptism for those witnessing Jesus'' resurrection.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
